Package gmavenplus.util

All utility classes

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DotGroovyFile
    This class exists solely to trick JavaStubCompilationUnit.addSource(java.io.File) into letting us use files that don't end in ".groovy"
    GroovyDocTemplateInfo
    This class was taken directly from the Groovy project because it's just a collection of Strings, but it wasn't available prior to Groovy 1.7 and we need it for Groovydoc generation.
    ReflectionUtils
    Inspired from https://src.springframework.org/svn/spring-framework/trunk/org.springframework.core/src/main/java/org/springframework/util/ReflectionUtils.java
